0last,any%20protestors%20from%20Hong%20Kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humanrightsfirst.org%2Fpress-release%2Fus-executive-order-unlikely-help-hong-kong-refugees%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWASHINGTON%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520While%2520the%2520president%2520last%2Cany%2520protestors%2520from%2520Hong%2520Kong&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=11858370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.humanrightsfirst.org/press-release/us-executive-order-unlikely-help-hong-kong-refugees#:~:text=WASHINGTON%20%E2%80%94%20While%20the%20president%20last,any%20protestors%20from%20Hong%20Kong</a><br />\n<br />\nPresident Trump 7 月 14 日, 簽咗個 Executive Order:<br />\n<strong>The President&rsquo;s Executive Order on Hong Kong Normalization</strong><br />\n<em>(k)  reallocate admissions within the refugee ceiling set by the annual Presidential Determination to residents of Hong Kong based on humanitarian concerns, to the extent feasible and consistent with applicable law; and<br />\n(l)  propose for my consideration any further actions deemed necessary and prudent to end special conditions and preferential treatment for Hong Kong.</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/presidents-executive-order-hong-kong-normalization/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2Fpresidents-executive-order-hong-kong-normalization%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=49d1bb2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/presidents-executive-order-hong-kong-normalization/</a>"},{"pid":"d139fdea193e3051bc463feb919d2ffa7190defd","tid":2176571,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:24:12.000Z","msg":"STEM major 可以OPT 3年<br />\n<br />\n抽多幾次"},{"pid":"b9ec56d97357a0f665a38b47d0282d93420e681b","tid":2176571,"uid":114463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0